Snake Block, the addictive puzzle game, is now available as a Chrome Extension. Immerse yourself in a challenging world of blocks and snakes right from your Chrome browser. Guide the snake to eat the blocks and grow longer while avoiding obstacles.

With the Snake Block Chrome Extension, you can experience the engaging gameplay and strategic thinking directly in your browser. Plan your moves carefully to navigate through increasingly complex levels and achieve high scores.

Whether you're a fan of puzzle games or enjoy testing your problem-solving skills, the Chrome Extension version of Snake Block offers a convenient and accessible way to enjoy this captivating game. Get ready to slither, strategize, and conquer the puzzle-filled world in this addictive game available at your fingertips.
